<tr style="text-align:center;">
<td width="30%" align="center" rowspan="1">Preceded&#160;by<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold"><a href="Chicago_White_Sox" title="Chicago White Sox">Chicago White Sox</a><br />
1906</span></td>
<td width="40%" style="text-align: center;" rowspan="1"><b>American League Champions<br />
